					<outline text="I'm forwarding this link to my readers, without comment, at this time. Please read it and give it your consideration. " created="Thu, 26 Jun 2008 00:58:55 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Shel Israel: &lt;a href=&quot;http://redcouch.typepad.com/weblog/2008/06/dealing-with-lo.html&quot;&gt;About Loren Feldman &amp; Michael Arrington&lt;/a&gt;." created="Thu, 26 Jun 2008 00:43:57 GMT"/>
