					</outline>
				<outline text="Reddit goes open source" created="Wed, 18 Jun 2008 16:17:06 GMT" type="outline">
					<outline text="&lt;img src=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2008/06/18/redditdude.gif&quot; width=&quot;57&quot; height=&quot;81&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; hspace=&quot;15&quot; vspace=&quot;5&quot; alt=&quot;A picture named redditdude.gif&quot;&gt;A very welcome &lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.reddit.com/2008/06/reddit-goes-open-source.html&quot;&gt;development&lt;/a&gt;, as I've written &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scripting.com/stories/2007/11/26/theNextStepInDiggClones.html&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; earlier, I am interested in one-off special micro-community news voting systems. " created="Wed, 18 Jun 2008 16:17:10 GMT"/>
