					<outline text="Click on the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/photos/scriptingnews/2552070576/sizes/l/&quot;&gt;pic&lt;/a&gt; above to get the full extent of the Times' (lack of) historic perspective." created="Wed, 04 Jun 2008 20:19:35 GMT"/>
