					<outline text="PS: This was inspired by a &lt;a href=&quot;http://friendfeed.com/e/4cb318f1-d83c-bc59-2595-288898f53b7e/United-is-cutting-100-flights-and-1600-jobs/&quot;&gt;thread&lt;/a&gt; started by Steve Rubel on FriendFeed. " created="Wed, 04 Jun 2008 13:24:05 GMT"/>
